data.title: Arnold Schwarzenegger News, Pictures, and Videos
data.meta_description: Get the latest and most updated news, videos, and photo galleries about Arnold Schwarzenegger
data.text:
Joseph Baena Channels Dad Arnold Schwarzenegger After Showcasing Bodybuilding Progress

Joseph Baena recently displayed his very toned upper body in a new Instagram video, where he looked like dad Arnold Schwarzenegger at the height of his bodybuilding career in the 1970s.

Joseph Baena Channels Dad Arnold Schwarzenegger While Competing in His First Triathlon

Joseph Baena celebrated his 26th birthday by competing in the Malibu Triathlon, posting a slew of photos that bare a striking resemblance to his dad Arnold Schwarzenegger.

Arnold Schwarzenegger's Cheating Scandal "Crushed" Maria Shriver

Arnold Schwarzenegger reflects on telling then-wife Maria Shriver he had welcomed a child with their housekeeper in his upcoming Netflix docuseries, "Arnold."

Arnold Schwarzenegger Recalls Moment He Told Maria Shriver He Fathered a Child With Housekeeper

Arnold Schwarzenegger reflected on the exact moment he told then-wife Maria Shriver he had welcomed a child with their housekeeper in his upcoming Netflix docuseries Arnold.

Would Joseph Baena Want to Act With Dad Arnold Schwarzenegger? He Says…

While attending the premiere of Arnold Schwarzenegger's new Netflix series FUBAR, Joseph Baena revealed if he'd be up for working with his father one day.

Arnold Schwarzenegger’s New Role as Netflix Boss Revealed

Arnold Schwarzenegger is putting his years of action-packed acting experience to good use, having just accepted a role at Netflix.

Arnold Schwarzenegger's Look-Alike Son Joseph Baena Breaks Down His Fitness Routine in Shirtless Workout

Joseph Baena's recent workout would make his dad, Arnold Schwarzenegger, proud. The bodybuilder and Dancing with the Stars alum broke down his fitness routine on Instagram.

Why Arnold Schwarzenegger Thinks He and Maria Shriver Deserve an Oscar for Their Divorce

Arnold Schwarzenegger said he and ex-wife Maria Shriver are "very proud" of how they approached their divorce and "the least amount of impact" it had on their four kids.

Joseph Baena Reveals How He Powered Past the Comments About Being Arnold Schwarzenegger's Son

Any child of a "high-succeeding parent" will feel pressured, Joseph Baena tells E! News. But putting in the work—on set, in business, at the gym—is how Arnold Schwarzenegger's son learned to thrive.

How Katherine Schwarzenegger Really Feels About Critics of Her and Husband Chris Pratt

Katherine Schwarzenegger shared how she has dealt with comments about herself and her family including dad Arnold Schwarzenegger and husband Chris Pratt, throughout the years.

Why Maria Shriver Went to a Convent After Arnold Schwarzenegger Breakup

Maria Shriver recalled traveling to a convent after ending her marriage to ex Arnold Schwarzenegger. Find out what she learned during her visit.

Dancing With the Stars: Gabby Windey and Wayne Brady Earn Perfect Scores on Prom Night

It was Prom Night on the Oct. 18 episode of Dancing With the Stars, which featured the first two perfect scores of the season. Find out who did well—and who went home.

DWTS Pro Daniella Karagach Will Not Dance In New Episode After Testing Positive for COVID-19

Ahead of the Sept. 26 episode of Dancing With the Stars, pro Daniella Karagach has tested positive for COVID-19. Find out how the show will address her absence.

Dancing With the Stars' Joseph Baena's Hollywood Role Model Isn't Who You'd Expect

Following the Dancing With the Stars premiere, Joseph Baena and partner Daniella Karagach caught up with reporters to tease what's to come in the ballroom.

Selma Blair Brings the Ballroom to Tears With Her Emotional Performance on Dancing With the Stars

On the Sept. 19 season premiere of Dancing With the Stars, Selma Blair made everybody cry and a Sex and the City favorite got sent home.

Why Joseph Baena Says His Fitness Might Actually Work Against Him on Dancing with the Stars

Joseph Baena is no stranger to breaking a sweat, but the fitness nut says his early Dancing with the Stars practice has been challenging. Find out what he told E! News about the experience.

One of Arnold Schwarzenegger's Sons Is Hitting the Dance Floor for DWTS Season 31

The upcoming season of Dancing with the Stars has added the son of Hollywood royalty. Find out which son of Arnold Schwarzenegger is taking aim at the Mirrorball Trophy.
